title: 820-3787 Fan goes high and laggish after 10 secs. Left Fin Stack Proximity failed in ASD test
message:
Hi all,

This is not a liquid dmg board.
Fan goes high and laggish. ASD test failed with Left Fin Stack Proximity.

SMBUS_SMC_0_S0_SDA AND SCL CLEAR 3.3V. GPUTHMSNS_THM_L IS 3.3V.

Missing GPUTHMSNS_ALERT_L. 0V.
I replaced Q5801,Q5803, U5850 still no luck.  DATA sheet says it requirs a pull up resistor to get the voltage.

Any idea?
